00:03:33.868 --> 00:03:36.070 position:30% line:83% align:start
Not one of us
can live on our own.

00:03:36.070 --> 00:03:38.705 position:7% line:83% align:start
@And yet, young or old, we're
all able to get through life

00:03:38.705 --> 00:03:40.673 position:16% line:83% align:start
