ago, the Earth was born in a
small corner

00:03:44.143 --> 00:03:47.612 position:16% line:89% align:start
of this vast universe...

00:03:47.612 --> 00:03:50.881 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]: Before I knew it,
several weeks had passed.

00:03:50.881 --> 00:03:53.282 position:24% line:83% align:start
As Nagisa entered
her third month,

00:03:53.282 --> 00:03:54.951 position:5% line:89% align:start
her morning sickness got worse.

00:03:54.951 --> 00:03:57.319 position:30% line:83% align:start
