It's no trouble at all.

00:04:04.959 --> 00:04:06.025 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm still sorry.

00:04:06.025 --> 00:04:07.794 position:13% line:89% align:start
Nothing to apologize for.

00:04:07.794 --> 00:04:10.496 position:21% line:83% align:start
We work together on
everything, remember?

00:04:11.897 --> 00:04:14.065 position:19% line:83% align:start
Have you had a chance
to eat anything today?

