much of an appetite.

00:04:16.333 --> 00:04:17.968 position:19% line:83% align:start
Is there some medicine
that would help,

00:04:17.968 --> 00:04:19.401 position:19% line:89% align:start
or that sort of thing?

00:04:19.401 --> 00:04:21.071 position:10% line:83% align:start
