00:04:24.939 --> 00:04:27.674 position:13% line:83% align:start
so I have to get my fluids
with ice cubes.

00:04:37.082 --> 00:04:38.984 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, wow, it's cold.

00:04:53.694 --> 00:04:57.397 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ah, sorry. Didn't mean to
wake you up. You feeling okay?

00:04:57.397 --> 00:04:59.465 position:19% line:89% align:start
Not too bad, I guess.

00:04:59.465 --> 00:05:00.466 position:30% line:89% align:start
@Good to hear.

00:05:00.466 --> 00:05:02.234 position:5% line:89% align:start
@Even if it's justúa little bit,

00:05:02.234 --> 00:05:03.935 position:27% line:83% align:start
@you should try
toúeat when you can.

00:05:05.203 --> 00:05:06.336 position:33% line:89% align:start
@Open wide.

00:05:07.805 --> 00:05:10.506 position:19% line:83% align:start
You had to make dinner
all by yourself, didn't you?

00:05:10.506 --> 00:05:13.176 position:5% line:83% align:start
@Oh, you could tell? Guessúthey
aren't very pretty, huh?

00:05:13.176 --> 00:05:16.545 position:10% line:83% align:start
I don't care what they look
like. Let me give it a try.

00:05:22.515 --> 00:05:24.450 position:24% line:89% align:start
Thanks, it's good!

00:05:26.920 --> 00:05:29.655 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]:
One again, time flew by.

00:05:29.655 --> 00:05:32.257 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was so wrapped up
in my daily life with Nagisa

00:05:32.257 --> 00:05:33.257 position:10% line:89% align:start
that I hardly even noticed.

00:05:33.257 --> 00:05:35.892 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa]: Good morning!

00:05:35.892 --> 00:05:37.794 position:21% line:83% align:start
You sure you should
be out of bed?

00:05:37.794 --> 00:05:40.496 position:5% line:83% align:start
@I'm fine; I'm actuallyúfeeling
a lot better today.

00:05:40.496 --> 00:05:41.931 position:27% line:83% align:start
