00:05:57.608 --> 00:05:59.577 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya]: Home birth?

00:05:59.577 --> 00:06:01.678 position:5% line:83% align:start
@Yeah, actually, I wasúthinking
about giving birth

00:06:01.678 --> 00:06:03.079 position:13% line:89% align:start
@right hereúin this room.

00:06:03.079 --> 00:06:04.981 position:21% line:83% align:start
Wow, you can really
do something like that?

00:06:04.981 --> 00:06:06.882 position:24% line:83% align:start
@Yesterday, when I
wasúat the hospital,

00:06:06.882 --> 00:06:09.750 position:7% line:83% align:start
@I picked up this brochureúfor
a maternity class.

00:06:09.750 --> 00:06:12.419 position:16% line:83% align:start
@It has an article about
mothersúwho gave birth at home

00:06:12.419 --> 00:06:15.289 position:24% line:83% align:start
@and I thought I'd
