much time with it

00:06:24.095 --> 00:06:26.663 position:7% line:83% align:start
right after it's born. That's
why I thought it might be nice

00:06:26.663 --> 00:06:28.966 position:7% line:89% align:start
if we did it this way instead.

00:06:28.966 --> 00:06:30.533 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hmmm...

00:06:34.469 --> 00:06:37.938 position:7% line:83% align:start
This is our home, so I thought
we should start our family here.

00:06:37.938 --> 00:06:41.075 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'd like to have my baby in
my own town, in my own room...

00:06:41.075 --> 00:06:43.343 position:27% line:89% align:start
where I belong.

00:06:43.343 --> 00:06:45.078 position:7% line:89% align:start
Do you think we could do that?

00:06:46.578 --> 00:06:49.081 position:24% line:83% align:start
