justúgonna complicate things,

00:07:06.327 --> 00:07:07.294 position:24% line:89% align:start
@don't you think?

00:07:07.294 --> 00:07:08.996 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I know what you mean;

00:07:08.996 --> 00:07:10.663 position:7% line:83% align:start
