about Nagisa's health.

00:07:10.663 --> 00:07:12.298 position:24% line:83% align:start
Still, she's seems
really set on it,

00:07:12.298 --> 00:07:14.165 position:5% line:89% align:start
so I'd like to do it if we can.

00:07:14.165 --> 00:07:17.202 position:5% line:83% align:start
I mean, assuming it doesn't put
her health at risk, of course.

00:07:17.202 --> 00:07:18.903 position:24% line:89% align:start
@[Sanae]ÚI agree.

00:07:18.903 --> 00:07:22.305 position:19% line:77% align:start
@You have to consider
