00:07:25.208 --> 00:07:28.210 position:5% line:83% align:start
@The nurse took Nagisa awayúfrom
me as soon as she was born.

00:07:28.210 --> 00:07:30.945 position:10% line:83% align:start
@Of course, Akio got to hold
herúa little bit later...

00:07:30.945 --> 00:07:33.347 position:16% line:77% align:start
@but that was only after
theúhospital staff said it was
okay.

00:07:33.347 --> 00:07:36.249 position:10% line:83% align:start
