00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:09.540 position:35% line:89% align:start
@[laughs]

00:08:09.540 --> 00:08:11.142 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]:
Wow, you two are some pair...

00:08:13.643 --> 00:08:16.079 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Sanae]: This is my friend Yagi.

00:08:16.079 --> 00:08:17.646 position:16% line:89% align:start
@She works as a midwife,

00:08:17.646 --> 00:08:18.713 position:13% line:83% align:start
@so I thought she mightúbe
