I'm sorry, Tomoya.

00:09:47.046 --> 00:09:49.948 position:7% line:77% align:start
@You know, this really reminds
meúof when we were in high
school.

00:09:49.948 --> 00:09:51.216 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:51.216 --> 00:09:52.884 position:10% line:83% align:start
