00:11:30.356 --> 00:11:32.258 position:13% line:83% align:start
If something bad happened,
then you should've told me!

00:11:32.258 --> 00:11:34.592 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sorry Tomoya... I didn't
want to bother you

00:11:34.592 --> 00:11:36.761 position:24% line:83% align:start
while you were at
work, that's all.

00:11:36.761 --> 00:11:38.196 position:13% line:89% align:start
At any rate, don't worry.

00:11:38.196 --> 00:11:39.796 position:21% line:83% align:start
The baby is still as
healthy as can be.

00:11:39.796 --> 00:11:42.165 position:10% line:89% align:start
[sighs] Well, that's good...

00:11:44.266 --> 00:11:46.835 position:13% line:83% align:start
Don't be afraid to call me
if anything else happens.

00:11:46.835 --> 00:11:48.803 position:21% line:83% align:start
@Just to be (extra)
careful, ústarting tomorrow,

00:11:48.803 --> 00:11:51.372 position:16% line:83% align:start
@I'll look after Nagisaú
til you get off of work.

00:11:51.372 --> 00:11:53.740 position:21% line:83% align:start
@That should take a
littleústress off of you, right?

00:11:53.740 --> 00:11:56.242 position:35% line:83% align:start
Yes ma'am.
I really appreciate it.

00:11:59.078 --> 00:12:02.713 position:16% line:83% align:start
@How are you feeling?úls
there anything you want?

00:12:02.713 --> 00:12:04.915 position:7% line:89% align:start
No, I have everything I need.

00:12:04.915 --> 00:12:06.749 position:7% line:89% align:start
