I'll try not to worry, myself.

00:12:17.058 --> 00:12:20.527 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't be afraid, Tomoya,
everything's gonna be fine.

00:12:20.527 --> 00:12:23.162 position:7% line:89% align:start
Yeah. You're right, of course.

00:12:23.162 --> 00:12:26.065 position:16% line:83% align:start
Whatever happens, we can
get through it together.

00:12:26.065 --> 00:12:29.334 position:10% line:83% align:start
